name: Vintage Gold Tone Flower Necklace
description:
I found this vintage gold tone 1950's textured flower at a Parisian flea market. The modern brass chain measures 18" and can be easily adjusted to make it a bit shorter. The repurposed flower pin is 2 3/4" in diameter and is in great condition. Together the chain and flower make a beautiful necklace and are measures 24 inches in total.

Please note there may be some slight imperfections due to the vintage nature of this item which adds to the charm of the necklace.

name: Vintage Pearl and Gold Flower Necklace
description:
Six vintage pearls nestled in the center of this intricate gold flower create a very unique focal point. Suspended on 18" of gold filled chain, this necklace is both delicate and dainty yet bold and striking: a lovely statement necklace for day or night. 

Please note there may be some slight imperfections due to the vintage nature of this item which adds to the charm of the necklace.

name: Vintage White Enamel and Gold Flower Necklace
description:
I sourced, designed and assembled this lovely white enamel flower necklace from a vintage flower pin which hangs from a 13" twisted link gold tone brass chain. The enamel flower is 3" in length and in great condition. Together the modern chain and repurposed vintage flower measure 16" in length. This white and gold flower necklace and is perfect to wear with a t-shirt or a dress as a statement necklace. I can customize the length of the chain if you prefer it to be shorter.

Please note there may be some slight imperfections due to the vintage nature of this item which add to the charm of the necklace.

name: Vintage Lucite Ball Gold Tone Long Necklace
description:
I created this 20" long statement necklace from recycled vintage textured chains accented by a 1980's Lucite ball filled with sparkly gold foil stars. The Lucite star ball is 2 inches in diameter and is super fun and exciting!! You'll definitely get noticed wearing this!

Please note there may be some slight imperfections due to the vintage nature of this item which adds to the charm of the necklace.

name: Vintage Spider Web Necklace with a Faceted Chrysoprase Bead
description:
I sourced, designed and assembled this spider web necklace. The necklace is made from a repurposed web earring accented by a sparkling rhinestone and hangs from a vintage light gold brass chain. A large faceted Chrysoprase bead adds a splash of color. The necklace measures 20 1/4" in length.

Please note there may be some slight imperfections due to the vintage nature of this item which adds to the charm of the necklace.

name: Repurposed Vintage Barrel Lock Necklace with Silver Tone Keys
description: A repurposed vintage Barrel Lock hangs from a 20" vintage chain accented by silver tone keys and Black and Cream Dalmatian Jasper.  Over the years, the combination for the silver lock was lost yet you might be the one to solve the mystery as it still spins and adds to the uniqueness of this vintage necklace. This long lock and key necklace will make the right out fit feel edgy either by itself or layered with additional long silver chains.

name: Vintage 70's Green Crystal Medallion Necklace
description:
I discovered this 70's Green Medallion hiding at a flea market under a bunch of junk. It just spoke to me! It makes a great statement necklace, paired with a modern brass large link chain. The medallion measures almost 2 1/2" in diameter and the chain is 20" long. The entire necklace is 22 1/2" long. 

Please note there may be some slight imperfections due to the vintage nature of this item which adds to the charm of the necklace.

name: Vintage Long Gold Tone Brass Necklace with Carnelian Beads
description:
I made this necklace from two different repurposed gold tone earrings connected by two 15mm orange red carnelian faceted beads and a brass gold tone chain. Together the modern decorative chain and the vintage earrings make a wonderful 20" necklace accented by 10 gold tone coins. To wear it, just place it over your head. No clasp needed! Perfect layered with more long gold tone chains or worn as a statement necklace on it's own.

Please note there may be some slight imperfections due to the vintage nature of this item which adds to the charm of the necklace.

name: Vintage Pewter Nymph Necklace with Silver Plated Chain
description:
This lovely necklace is 20" long with a beautiful pendant of a nameless woodland nymph playing her harp in the garden. The vintage pewter nymph pendant has not lost any of its detail over the years and is quite striking to admire. What will you name this woodland maiden?

Please note there may be some slight imperfections due to the vintage nature of this item which adds to the charm of the necklace.

name: Repurposed Silver Plated Lariat Necklace
description:
The lovely drop of the necklace has vintage chandelier crystals accented by semi precious stones including quartz, jet beads and a 10mm gray shell pearl as well as two silver tone decorative shells. This 19" lariat necklace is made from modern silver plated and sterling chains as well as vintage heavy link chain. Two 10mm shell pearls attach the silver links together. Worn over a dress or casually with jeans, this piece is sure to make a statement.

Please note there may be some slight imperfections due to the vintage nature of this item which adds to the charm of the necklace.

name: Long Thai Buddha Double Necklace with Gold Sun
description: What better way to have Peace and Protection than from a Buddha that was blessed by Thai Monks. The Buddha I sourced is is encased and sealed with a gold toned frame and is said to represent enlightenment while the gold sun i added above will bring sunshine to anyone's life. This double strand necklace measures 38" in length and will empower you all day long.

name: Vintage Enamel Camel Necklace
description:
I spied this 3" by 2.5" brass enameled camel at a market in Paris and couldn't leave without her. I dangled her from a 30" vintage brass chain and added a wonderful black and gold glass bead to top off her hump. The camel is beautifully finished on both sides and spins around. This necklace will really make a statement. This is one of my favorite finds!

Please note there may be some slight imperfections due to the vintage nature of this item which adds to the charm of the necklace.

name: Brass Gold Tone Star Filigree Necklace with Faceted Garnet Drop
description: For a more subtle look, check out this 2 1/4" filigree star adorned by a faceted garnet hanging from two delicate gold fill chains. The necklace measures 16" in length and is a great addition to any outfit.

name: Vintage Parisian Poodle Necklace
description:
Bonjour from Paris! Don't you just love how this little French pooch is begging for attention? This cute vintage poodle pendant hangs from a 24" silver plated oxidized chain. Her sparkly red crystal eye really makes her stand out.

Please note there may be some slight imperfections due to the vintage nature of this item which adds to the charm of the necklace.

name: Vintage Gold Tone Crystal Leaf Necklace
description:
This will get you noticed! From the 18" vintage gold tone brass chain dangles a lovely leaf pendant. Gold tone textured leaves are accented by turquoise and bright green almond-shaped crystals. This necklace will surely make the right outfit look wonderful!

Please note there may be some slight imperfections due to the vintage nature of this item which adds to the charm of the necklace.

name: Vintage Flower and Silver Bird Necklace
description:
This lovely vintage cream flower necklace accented with a silver tone bird will certainly make you sing! Clear crystals found in the center of each flower also encrust the bird's wings and tail. I dangled the 2" in diameter flower pendant from a 20" double link brass chain which will complete any outfit and make you look even more beautiful than you already are! Tweet tweet.

Please note there may be some slight imperfections due to the vintage nature of this item which adds to the charm of the necklace.

name: Vintage Gold and Crystal Bow Necklace
description:
I loved this textured gold tone bow the moment i found it. The bow is 2" long by 1" tall with clear crystals and a textured finish. It hangs delicately on a simple yet fun 18" long oval link gold chain. Perfect to wear for the holidays or anytime you're feeling special. I really love this piece. Enjoy!

Please note there may be some slight imperfections due to the vintage nature of this item which adds to the charm of the necklace.

name: Vintage Delicate Gold Bow Necklace
description:
A delicate bow 1.5" long by .5" dangles from a 18" circle embellished brass chain. Five clear sparkly crystals add shine to the tiny gold tone bow. Perfect for a little black dress or with a pair of jeans.

Please note there may be some slight imperfections due to the vintage nature of this item which adds to the charm of the necklace.

name: Retro Black Enameled Butterfly Necklace
description:
I enjoyed sourcing, designing and assembling this great retro black enameled butterfly necklace. I used two different types of chain to balance this piece out: double link chain and a sterling rolo chain which together measure 16" in length. 3 black "jet beads" complete the necklace.

Please note there may be some slight imperfections due to the vintage nature of this item which adds to the charm of the necklace.

name: Bone Octopus Necklace with Gold Chains and Bone Beads
description: The octopus is symbolic for mystery, intelligence and insight. I sourced this beautifully carved cream bone octopus with textured tentacles and small black eyes especially to create a necklace for protection and good luck. I added two varying gold plated chains to the handmade octopus necklace. These chains create a 16" necklace which is accompanied by two bone beads about 1/4" in diameter and a gold filled circle. Celebrate your vision with this beautiful creature from the sea!

name: Vintage Silver Plated Goddess Diana Medallion Necklace
description:
I stumbled upon this Roman goddess Diana medallion at a tiny antique fair in Sonoma, CA. Diana was the Roman goddess of hunting and the moon and was associated with wild animals and woodland. Together the modern silver plated chains and the vintage medallion make a wonderful 20" long statement necklace. Each unique chain is connect together by a large gray 15mm shell pearl to enhance the necklace. For a different look, layer it with other long silver chains.

Please note there may be some slight imperfections due to the vintage nature of this item which adds to the charm of the necklace.

name: Vintage Gold Tone Dahlia Necklace
description:
I discovered this 2" in diameter 1950's brooch in Northern California and knew I had to show it off somehow. The textured flower petals needed nothing more to embellish them so I showcased them at the end of this 20" long gold plated large link chain. The pendant really is a bold statement piece that is quite pretty in person.

Please note there may be some slight imperfections due to the vintage nature of this item which adds to the charm of the necklace.

name: Brass Filigree Star Necklace with Pink Faceted Andesine Labradorite Drop
description: For a more subtle look, check out this 2 1/4" filigree star adorned by a faceted pink andesine labradorite hanging from two delicate gold fill chains. The necklace measures 16" in length and is a great addition to any outfit.

name: Amethyst and Silver Cascading Necklace
description: This handmade 18" silver plated necklace with cascading drops of beautiful large square amethyst beads connected with silver tone wire defines a statement necklace. 19 stones in cascading formation measures 5" in length and will be a lovely addition to your Boho chic outfit. It's true that  amethyst and silver make such a unique timeless necklace.

name: Vintage Smokey Amber Crystal and Pearl Necklace
description:
Amber naturally imbues the color of sunshine with yellow for the midday sun and orange for fiery sunsets. This large sultry amber crystal and brown pearl necklace is sure to add a hit of sophistication to any outfit. Complete with sparkly clear crystals and a delicate gold filled 16" chain and clasp, this crystal piece really radiates. 

Please note there may be some slight imperfections due to the vintage nature of this item which adds to the charm of the necklace.

name: Vintage Silver Rose Necklace with Semi Precious Stones
description:
After looking for months, I finally found the perfect vintage silver tone rose pin to complete this necklace. The repurposed pin is the focal point of the necklace. There are two different types of modern silver plated chain used to create this 16"' necklace. One shows large and small circles as links which connect the  twisted oval linked chain by 3 large faceted 10mm clear quartz stones. Two gray large 12mm shell pearls connect the other side of the necklace. The necklace easily goes on over your head.

Please note there may be some slight imperfections due to the vintage nature of this item which adds to the charm of the necklace.

name: Red Coral Necklace
description: When i discovered this unique red coral i was amazed at the tiny sea shell remains Mother Nature accidentally placed in it's grip! I just had to have it; something i will never ever see again. I carefully wrapped brass wire around the red coral to secure it safely to the 22" solid brass chain and finished with a gold tone lobster clasp. This really is a lovely piece and will sure to start a conversation about that tiny little shell nesting in the coral.

name: Vintage Cross Pendant Necklace w/ Cabochons and Faceted Stones
description:
I connected a lovely 18" new twisted link brass chain to a very special vintage 2" cross to create this one of a kind statement necklace. With 8 purple Cabochons, 4 faceted green stones, 12 clear sparkling stones and 4 faux pearls, this piece really sparkles in the light! The repurposed purple and green brass cross necklace is a beautiful addition to your outfit day or night.

Please note there may be some slight imperfections due to the vintage nature of this item which adds to the charm of the necklace.

name: Vintage Gray Swarovski Crystal with Ornate Gold Tone Pendant
description:
Seven lucky crystals will sure to bring you fame and fortune with this 18" necklace. A repurposed vintage treasure I discovered measuring 2" in diameter is the focal point of this piece. I added a gray vintage Swarovski crystal to connect the pendant to the chain of large brass links. Certainly makes a lovely addition to any outfit!

Please note there may be some slight imperfections due to the vintage nature of this item which adds to the charm of the necklace.

name: Vintage Silver Plated Lariat Necklace
description:
The lovely drop of the necklace has vintage chandelier crystals accented by semi precious stones including quartz, jet beads and a 10mm gray shell pearl as well as two silver tone decorative shells. This 19" lariat necklace is made from modern silver plated and sterling chains as well as vintage heavy link chain. Two 10mm shell pearls attach the silver links together. Worn over a dress or casually with jeans, this piece is sure to make a statement.

Please note there may be some slight imperfections due to the vintage nature of this item which adds to the charm of the necklace.

name: Filigree Brass Gold Tone Heart Locket with Vintage Cream Flower
description: At the end of this 20" brass chain hangs a hinged 1.5" gold tone brass heart locket. I added a pretty vintage cream flower to the heart. A perfect little place to keep a picture of your loved one.
